{"tid":298861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"番兼職遇到仆街老闆","createTime":"2017-06-26T15:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T17:20:57.000Z","uid":24342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c6a788ecf15d18642227e99cba160520b39ccfc","tid":298861,"uid":24342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:17:45.000Z","msg":"朋友經歷<br />\n聽到覺得心酸 幫佢訴下苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個仆街老闆一定要簽三個月約 <br />\n我朋友本身覺得冇咩問題就簽咗<br />\n點知佢老闆唔撚比佢請假 <br />\n請一請假就會比老闆要脅扣佣金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔止請假麻煩 連辭職都要早一個月講 <br />\n做唔夠三個月仲要賠幾千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都有番兼職 我份兼職頭三個月辭職淨係要早一個星期講 仲唔洗賠錢 <br />\n<br />\n番到去話題 <br />\n個老闆去到第二個月就冇編過我朋友番工<br />\n本來編咗幾日番工 突然之間cut哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔炒我個fd因爲佢未過試用期炒人要賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個fd仲有次番工𠝹到手 𠝹甩忽肉流哂血 <br />\n佢老尾個老闆唔比佢即刻去睇醫生 <br />\n遲咗睇醫生 本身可以縫針但係遲咗就已經冇得縫<br />\n<br />\n本身我個fd都幾鍾意番 但係個老闆不停咁剝削佢 <br />\n成日話要扣獎金又cut更又唔理佢嘅安全 <br />\n佢已經對份工冇咩希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真<br />\n學生哥搵份兼職開心搵下錢都遇到咁現實嘅老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279da175b2febe02a86900959f5e5f17589feeac","tid":298861,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:21:07.000Z","msg":"你FD on9<br />\n唔俾佢睇醫生就唔去睇<br />\n咁聽話<br />\n叫你食屎又食啊<br />\n俾我就即刻衝去睇<br />\n理撚得佢"},{"pid":"6711cd7acd721c7b79bffd437b99e8c677946b8d","tid":298861,"uid":24342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你FD on9<br />\n唔俾佢睇醫生就唔去睇<br />\n咁聽話<br />\n叫你食屎又食啊<br />\n俾我就即刻衝去睇<br />\n理撚得佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講嗰陣間舖得佢一個 <br />\n如果佢走就要閂舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3bd9dd351704dc85222c3de0172db0fdf61096","tid":298861,"uid":94457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"世界太多仆街 要識保護自己<br />\n好漢不吃眼前虧<br />\n唔好期望有人會幫你出頭"},{"pid":"ddc69dfe6b7a29c8e2ca7943e28699626bf82147","tid":298861,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:27:48.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"281d85c3e5d17a50dce3ffabba99f3fee7085dfa","tid":298861,"uid":24342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世界太多仆街 要識保護自己<br />\n好漢不吃眼前虧<br />\n唔好期望有人會幫你出頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我只能祝佢下次搵工搵個好啲嘅老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6b31dab6ea49eb440c111e89fa35232970f767","tid":298861,"uid":64293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"1.佢無睇清楚份約先簽架咩？<br />\n2唔係未過試用期唔洗1個月通知（僱主僱員都係）？<br />\n3.爆晒缸都唔去處理 傻架？<br />\n定係我認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c97e119600e858fda0bc761d44bc030131054b","tid":298861,"uid":24342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台式飲品店gc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a36981fbf2238a89cfff69d896b0733e978e8c6","tid":298861,"uid":24342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.佢無睇清楚份約先簽架咩？<br />\n2唔係未過試用期唔洗1個月通知（僱主僱員都係）？<br />\n3.爆晒缸都唔去處理 傻架？<br />\n定係我認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有睇過佢份約 完全係唔公平合約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔明點解佢要簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n爆缸好似係指爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo