 />\n叫你食屎又食啊<br />\n俾我就即刻衝去睇<br />\n理撚得佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講嗰陣間舖得佢一個 <br />\n如果佢走就要閂舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑撚咗<br />\n閂鋪咪閂舖囉<br />\n間鋪搵錢緊要定自己身體緊要啊<br />\n咁戇鳩嘅野都講得岀口嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1969b0b25489895108f29fd4f7d322c984d4f512","tid":298861,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:00:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你FD on9<br />\n唔俾佢睇醫生就唔去睇<br />\n咁聽話<br />\n叫你食屎又食啊<br />\n俾我就即刻衝去睇<br />\n理撚得佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講嗰陣間舖得佢一個 <br />\n如果佢走就要閂舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑撚咗<br />\n閂鋪咪閂舖囉<br />\n間鋪搵錢緊要定自己身體緊要啊<br />\n咁戇鳩嘅野都講得岀口嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係我<br />\n我會同老細講:我手指爆哂血，要去睇急症，一係你即刻落返嚟睇鋪，一係你即刻搵人嚟頂我，一係我就咁close"},{"pid":"a88bfe3dc8f4f4863d16c9d93283bcecb225cce6","tid":298861,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>世界太多仆街 要識保護自己<br />\n好漢不吃眼前虧<br />\n唔好期望有人會幫你出頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我只能祝佢下次搵工搵個好啲嘅老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只通夠講10個老闆9個都仆街<br />\n自己醒定啲喇"},{"pid":"297620c35532e9f2fb9d708d3b10689d14ddf4bf","tid":298861,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>世界太多仆街 要識保護自己<br />\n好漢不吃眼前虧<br />\n唔好期望有人會幫你出頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我只能祝佢下次搵工搵個好啲嘅老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只能夠講10個老闆9個都仆街<br />\n自己醒定啲喇</blockquote>"},{"pid":"64257c9788c1c0f1e861bb679996206094e2e27a","tid":298861,"uid":28844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1.佢無睇清楚份約先簽架咩？<br />\n2唔係未過試用期唔洗1個月通知（僱主